---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="BeachBride privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information."
  canonical="https://beachbride.com/privacy-policy/"
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: April 2026</p>

  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <p>
      BeachBride ("we," "us," or "our") operates BeachBride.com. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share information when you use our site and services.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name and email address (when you use our destination quiz or contact form)</li>
      <li>Phone number, wedding date, guest count, and budget (when you request vendor matching)</li>
      <li>Business information (when you register as a vendor)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We also collect usage data automatically, including IP address, browser type, pages visited, and referring URLs via analytics tools.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To send your personalized destination guide</li>
      <li>To match you with relevant wedding vendors (only if you complete Stage 2 of our quiz)</li>
      <li>To send our email newsletter and planning tips (you can unsubscribe anytime)</li>
      <li>To improve our content and services</li>
      <li>To respond to your inquiries</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>
      We share your lead information (name, email, phone, wedding details) with matched vendors only when you explicitly request vendor matching through our full quiz. We do not sell your data to third parties.
    </p>
    <p>
      We use third-party services including Mailgun (email delivery), Sendy (email marketing), Cloudflare (hosting), and analytics providers. These services have their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      BeachBride participates in affiliate programs with resorts, jewelry retailers, and travel services. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. We disclose affiliate relationships in relevant content.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      We use cookies and similar tracking technologies for analytics and to remember your preferences. You can control cookies through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information by emailing <a href="mailto:hello@beachbride.com">hello@beachbride.com</a>. You may also unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time using the link in any email we send.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:hello@beachbride.com">hello@beachbride.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
